{"tid":513154,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"少少人露營群 (新手老手都歡迎)","createTime":"2017-12-29T08:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T10:30:56.000Z","uid":68705,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fb269b120cdfa1f8f75794be290e4a14f878d855","tid":513154,"uid":68705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T08:44:30.000Z","msg":"一個少少人但多多趣既Group<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開左已經一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 固定每月一定有一次露營會搞到<br />\n<br />\n歡迎一啲對露營有興趣既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而希望入得群既都係一啲高質露營友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只要有興趣既人都會考慮<br />\n而群組都唔會太多人,盡量唔想有人比人無視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而搞露營既日子大多都係星期六去到星期日, 但唔會紅日或特別日子搞, 希望大家理解<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項:<br />\n<br />\n1. 入群前一定會經過篩選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 希望大家係抱住黎放鬆黎玩既心情入黎,唔好太過認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要認真對待既係個大自然, 遵守無痕露營呢啲基本既原則<br />\n<br />\n3. 盡可能出席群聚, 時間方面可以大家夾, 潛水+每次群聚都唔出就唔好怪我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要同你Say byebye<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 露營必須酒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩都可以有商有量，歡迎隨時搵我比任何意見/建議 <br />\n<br />\n有興趣加入既請填<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/pBy5BxR6P0GreOr63\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FpBy5BxR6P0GreOr63&d=WEX6p1p09bNIMuynU0Yvef%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a36e6383\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/pBy5BxR6P0GreOr63</a>"},{"pid":"7a2eff3e6683a42341580c40b0e529e1cc9cad23","tid":513154,"uid":57962,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:02:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d8d81898a21938531c8c9ab8da58774d01f7b5f","tid":513154,"uid":68705,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:35:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote> 4. 露營必須酒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直接開房大雜交咪算囉<br />\n<br />\n又篩選又剩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為左篩走你呢種煩膠 要既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c725b2e279b06013a5aca586b63425eb19b6133","tid":513154,"uid":57962,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:38:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bdab0f531b38b38613d518275737e861838e50fa","tid":513154,"uid":68705,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T12:03:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote> 4. 露營必須酒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直接開房大雜交咪算囉<br />\n<br />\n又篩選又剩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為左篩走你呢種煩膠 要既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>跌落地都要拿番渣沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肉酸到...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n是但你點講啦 <br />\n走啦 唔好搞咁多野啦<br />\n又無搞著你 唔岩咪返出去囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b1b50c8dfc8ea647261af24b3e84083c1e3426","tid":513154,"uid":68705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T19:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0463cb08885c04a153933ae751c7865deaab6b4","tid":513154,"uid":1748,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T09:36:24.000Z","msg":"露營同自己fd露得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇樓主個格都係狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要必須酒"},{"pid":"06ee794c0cdb74e0fe485c790bbb9e6ca31abadb","tid":513154,"uid":68705,"lik